g src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/f1135e7c5b6ea8b5f4608a5375882814/ce066891727f50cb-9b/s400x600/84e79a5b8efc432c45804f3934c7925389db9285.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Ff1135e7c5b6ea8b5f4608a5375882814%2Fce066891727f50cb-9b%2Fs400x600%2F84e79a5b8efc432c45804f3934c7925389db9285.gifv&h=b7f3f278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/52cbd9742d233ddb7948bd17b42938a3/ce066891727f50cb-4b/s400x600/816837e544a65d3fe437c8643f4a93c23bfb9c0b.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F52cbd9742d233ddb7948bd17b42938a3%2Fce066891727f50cb-4b%2Fs400x600%2F816837e544a65d3fe437c8643f4a93c23bfb9c0b.gifv&h=61b905ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:13:32.000Z","msg":"塊面做乜事"},{"pid":"9c4bbc7cdfffda5fb9dfb135805ac4832c8d1968","tid":1777582,"uid":187098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74042bc12bbb261007f1c1b06127360f6019780a","tid":1777582,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=444bf1eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"1c334c3077299bdcce7e17e44e4c1336e0260294","tid":1777582,"uid":30944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"93bc52ab52718c07fc86147d534ca32c5bd33b68","tid":1777582,"uid":195601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:46:55.000Z","msg":"pull"}],"pinned":{"pid":"66ad341733be07c2fd836f890fc14658b4d1a514","tid":1777582,"uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"黑色XX給她的意義 是一生奉獻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_205/and1211_1456273409689smIIB_GIF/1cfc1a54c7ef44d1.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogfiles.pstatic.net%2F20160224_205%2Fand1211_1456273409689smIIB_GIF%2F1cfc1a54c7ef44d1.gif&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=e84b54d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_205/and1211_1456273409689smIIB_GIF/1cfc1a54c7ef44d1.gif</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/kI7YUQD.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkI7YUQD.gif&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=3e05dddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/kI7YUQD.gif</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_298/and1211_1456273411797yTCT0_GIF/219481b184984867.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogfiles.pstatic.net%2F20160224_298%2Fand1211_1456273411797yTCT0_GIF%2F219481b184984867.gif&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6a1ddde5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_298/and1211_1456273411797yTCT0_GIF/219481b184984867.gif</a>"}}